                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "西风剑术 · 宗室"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">元素战技</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，如果本角色未附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冷酷之心</span>，则使其附属<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冷酷之心</span>。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/78b526224710dda639b49972145339a9_2449723080912769412.png",
                "id": "talent62616",
                "key": "冰潮的涡旋",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰潮的涡旋"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">元素爆发</span></p><p>造成2点<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素伤害</span>，召唤<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">光降之剑</span><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">。</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/72b7716be67efac4ec94efde16957180_5577649314750523264.png",
                "id": "talent99186",
                "key": "凝浪之光剑",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "凝浪之光剑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">召唤物</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">优菈使用「普通攻击」或「元素战技」时：</span>此牌积累2点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「能量层数」</span>，但是优菈不会获得充能。</p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">结束阶段：</span>弃置此牌，造成3点<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">物理伤害</span>；每有1点<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「能量层数」</span>，都使此伤害+1。</p><p>（影响此牌<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「可用次数」</span>的效果会作用于<span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">「能量层数」</span>。）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_651273052969626595.png",
                "id": "talent15980",
                "key": "光降之剑",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/24/88072335/3f07051befd3fcb50000df92021710d6_6454578419161040334.png",
                "title": "光降之剑"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>附着冰元素，可发生元素反应：</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">火元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">融化</span>：本伤害+2</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">雷元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">超导</span>：本伤害+1，对目标以外的所有敌方角色造成1点穿透伤害</p><p>【<span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">冰元素</span>+<span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">水元素</span>】<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">冻结</span>：本伤害+1，使目标本回合无法行动（受到物理或火元素伤害后提前解除，但是伤害+2）</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/88072335/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_4031943694369338436.png",
                "id": "talent79504",
                "key": "冰元素伤害",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "冰元素伤害"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">物理伤害</span></strong></p><p>物理伤害不会附着元素，也不会发生元素反应。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">冷酷之心</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">状态</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">所附属角色使用冰潮的涡旋时：</span>移除此状态，使本次伤害+3。</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">可用次数</span></strong></p><p>此牌效果触发后，会消耗1次<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>；</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">可用次数</span>耗尽后，立刻弃置此牌。</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/02/26/88072335/07bae546ac7c69ef6402170b283840c5_7765288967406384052.png",
